# Employee Portal — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A modern employee portal with **all 15 requested technologies** integrated and verified:

| # | Technology | Integration | Key File(s) |
|---|-----------|-------------|-------------|
| 1 | ✅ **Next.js 16** | Framework, Turbopack, App Router | [next.config.ts](file:///d:/oppp/next.config.ts) |
| 2 | ✅ **TypeScript** | All source files | [tsconfig.json](file:///d:/oppp/tsconfig.json) |
| 3 | ✅ **Clerk** | `ClerkProvider` (conditional), middleware | [layout.tsx](file:///d:/oppp/src/app/layout.tsx), [middleware.ts](file:///d:/oppp/src/middleware.ts) |
| 4 | ✅ **Sentry** | Client/server/edge configs, conditional wrapper | `sentry.*.config.ts`, [next.config.ts](file:///d:/oppp/next.config.ts) |
| 5 | ✅ **Tailwind CSS v4** | CSS-first `@theme` with oklch colors | [globals.css](file:///d:/oppp/src/app/globals.css) |
| 6 | ✅ **shadcn-ui** | 15 Radix UI components | `src/components/ui/` |
| 7 | ✅ **Zod** | 4 validation schemas | `src/lib/schemas.ts` |
| 8 | ✅ **Zustand** | 2 stores (notifications, sidebar) | `src/store/` |
| 9 | ✅ **Nuqs** | URL search params on Announcements | `announcements-client.tsx` |
| 10 | ✅ **TanStack Tables** | 3 admin data tables | `admin/users`, `admin/announcements`, `admin/audit-log` |
| 11 | ✅ **React Hook Form** | Profile + Manage Users forms | `profile/page.tsx`, `admin/users/page.tsx` |
| 12 | ✅ **kbar** | ⌘K command palette | `kbar-provider.tsx` |
| 13 | ✅ **ESLint** | Configured in `eslint-config-next` | `eslint.config.mjs` |
| 14 | ✅ **Husky** | Pre-commit hook → lint-staged | `.husky/pre-commit` |
| 15 | ✅ **Prettier** | Code formatting with lint-staged | `.prettierrc` |

> [!NOTE]
> **Clerk** and **Sentry** use conditional wrappers — they activate automatically when you add your API keys to `.env.local`. Copy `.env.example` to get started.

