## Pages (9 total)

| Page | Route | Features |
|------|-------|----------|
| Dashboard | `/dashboard` | Stat cards, announcements, activity timeline |
| Announcements | `/announcements` | Search + Nuqs URL filters |
| Notifications | `/notifications` | Tabs, mark-read (Zustand) |
| Profile | `/profile` | React Hook Form + Zod validation |
| Settings | `/settings` | Theme picker, notification toggles |
| Analytics | `/analytics` | Recharts area/bar charts, table |
| Manage Users | `/admin/users` | TanStack table, RHF+Zod dialog |
| Manage Announcements | `/admin/announcements` | TanStack table, CRUD |
| Audit Log | `/admin/audit-log` | Action filters, IP display |

