## Getting Started

```bash
# 1. Copy env template and add your API keys
cp .env.example .env.local

# 2. Start dev server
npm run dev

# 3. Available scripts
npm run format        # Format all files with Prettier
npm run lint          # ESLint check
npm run format:check  # Verify formatting
```
